The paper discusses the need for traceability in data ecosystems, which is a key concern in database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the need for accountability in data-driven and artificial intelligence systems, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a conceptual design for a model, which involves the architecture and implementation of a gateway, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
